posts.title: Surf Excel
posts.productDesc: The Surf Excel Quick Wash Detergent Powder is one of the leading detergents in the market. It is a superfine and strong powder that acts like a blue, bleach and lemon all together.

posts.title: Boost More 3X Stamina Nutrition Drink Powder
posts.productDesc: Boost is India's leading malt-based Health Food Drink in a chocolate flavor- a nourishing beverage to be consumed as part of your healthy daily diet and exercise plan.

posts.title: GRB Ghee
posts.productDesc: GRB is 100% pure and provides the taste of homemade ghee. It is a staple product across every South-Indian home and is synonymous for purity, aroma and taste. Our age old food wisdom has always been true to the core when they said ghee is good for health. No meal is complete without a dollop of pure desi ghee it. A scoop of ghee on steaming rice not only enriches the meal, but also provides a soothing flavour and healthy aroma to your everyday food. Made from pure cow's milk and packed specially, GRB GHEE is a must on your dining table and kitchen shelves

posts.title: Dettol Antiseptic Liquid
posts.productDesc: An iconic home essential for generations, Dettol Antiseptic Liquid is a holistic use product used for protection against germs that has been recommended by medical professionals and trusted by mothers. Launched in India in 1933, Dettol has been the trusted partner of health, for millions of mothers across the country, to protect their family by preventing illnesses and infections.

posts.title: Aashirvaad Superior Mp Atta
posts.productDesc: ITC - one of the most eminent names in food products and FMCG market, introduced this AASHIRVAAD range of food products. The Whole Wheat Atta was introduced in 27th May, 2002 and it claims to consist of 100% wheat and without any mixture of white flour.
